::DarkMouse::

She loked at Terrorsaur as he walked around her.
She glared at him.  She hated him.  She decided that if he was ever in 
trouble, she would turn off her comm-link and ignore him.  She went back to 
her console and completed her reports.  She strted thinking about her 
programming.  She hated this servent programming. She wanted to be more of a 
fighter and less of a maintenance bot.

---------Original Message---------
From: Talon Harvilicz  <wilddance_mare@h...>
Date: Fri Jun 30, 2000 2:36pm
Subject: Neo Beast Wars


Terrorsaur:


Terrorsaur couldn't stop growling at the mouse-bot. She was nothing but a
servant to what he saw. What good was she? All that she did was give him
energon that he didn't want. What a waste of bot!

He transformed to his robot mode and walked widely around her. He needed
something to do, but he wasn't going to ask that female bot.

He looked around. Where was that other flier?
